## GitHub Operations

```bash
# Clone the repo (first time)
gh repo clone bluefishforsale/homelab /tmp/homelab-fix

# Create fix branch
git checkout -b fix/<service>-<description>

# Open issue
gh issue create --repo bluefishforsale/homelab --title "[homelab-ops] ..." --body "..."

# Open PR
gh pr create --repo bluefishforsale/homelab --title "[homelab-ops] ..." --body "Fixes #<issue>" --base main

# Check CI status
gh run list --repo bluefishforsale/homelab --limit 5

# Notify terrac
# Send Discord DM with PR link
```

